2006-10-08 01:06 UTC+0100 Miguel Angel Marchuet <miguelangel@marchuet.net>
  + source\rdd\bmdbfcdx\bmdbfcdx1.c
  + source\rdd\bmdbfcdx\makefile
  + source\include\hbbmdbfcdx.h
  * makefile.bc
  * makefile.dc
  * makefile.gc
  * makefile.pc
  * makefile.vc
  * makefile.wc
  * config\dir.cf
   + First release of new rdd BMDBFCDX.
     The intention of this new RDD is to implement command post native behavior of clipper respect to the optimization of filters.
     System of Static Bitmap Filters is implemented until the moment.
     It is to implement a system of indexing in memory of filters and an optimization of the expressions of filters taking
     advantage of multiscopes on index to partially solve the expressions of the filter.
     Already implemented MULTIFILTER  Slope to implement MULTISCOPE

     Especific RDD functions:
      BM_DbSeekWild( cToSeekWithWildCard )
      BM_DbSetFilterArray( aRegisters )
      BM_Turbo( lOnOff )  (delicated function only recomended to create filters or local temporary index)
      aRegisters := BM_DbGetFilterArray()
      BM_DbSetFilterArrayAdd( aRegistersToAddToFilter )
      BM_DbSetFilterArrayDel ( aRegistersToDelFromFilter )

