2006-09-26 01:11 UTC-0800 Brian Hays <bhays at abacuslaw.com>
  * contrib/rdd_ads/adsfunc.c
    * removed dead code from AdsConnect60
    * fixed AdsDDGetUserProperty arg validation and buffer sizing
      (thanks to Luiz Culik)

    ! Notice change in parameters!!
      adsddGetUserProperty("Username", nPropertyID, @cProperty, nConnectionHandle)
      It's no longer necessary to allocate a buffer in prg code nor
      pass the length of that buffer, BUT cProperty must be passed by reference.
      nConnectionHandle was 5th arg before, now it's the 4th.

  * tests/datad.prg
    * added test for above

