2006-09-19 13:48 UTC-0800 Brian Hays <bhays at abacuslaw.com>
  * contrib/rdd_ads/ads1.c
    * fixed ADT creation bug with > 450 fields

  * include/hbextern.ch
    * added support for ifdef ADS to load adsexternal.ch (for xbscript)

  + utils/xbscript/bld_ads.bat
    * to build xbscript with ADS linked in

  * utils/xbscript/xbscript.prg

    * Changed HELP display to show XBSCRIPT instead of "PP"
        also added -S description
    * added support for ifdef ADS to load those rdds
    ! added -S switch to stay in DOT prompt mode after executing code

      This is a pretty cool feature. You can set up a batch file
      to call xbscript MyStartupStuff.prg -S
      and set default rdd to whatever, load lots of databases with
      relations into different workareas, and have the entire
      environment set up when you get the dot prompt.


