  * source/vm/codebloc.c
    * Raise error on possible GPF trap in hb_codeblockGetVar()
    /*
       Should never happen with valid block, I wonder if we should not use an ASSERT()
       macro instead. Same for other pedantic GPF traps which should never realy happen.
       This could improve performance in NON DEBUG builds.
    */

