2006-07-27 09:30 UTC-0300 Luiz Rafael Culik<luiz at xharbour.com.br>
  * include/hbset.h
    include/hbtrace.h
    ! exported some symbols for dll
  * source/common/hbtrace.c
    source/rtl/set.c
