  + xharbour/source/rtl/gtgui/gtgui.c
    + added GTGUI GT driver - it supports TONE and CLIPBOARD functionality
      only and is hacked to overload the default GT driver in multi GT
      compilation to make some Windows users happy ;-)
      Such GT driver also exists in Harbour.

